I can recommend the candidate for a client interview, but with the following comments:

Pros
1. excellent presentation with emphasis on teamwork
2. talks well and demonstrates self-management. 
3. Excellent knowledge of design processes. 
4. Good demonstration of UI skills.

Cons 

These minuses should be worked out for the client interview!

1. Prepare at least two cases for demonstration (CRM and Mobile)
2. Show UX artifacts.
3. Demonstrate the case of floating design processes
4. Prepare a library to show the client
5. When showing the case, focus on the distribution of responsibilities in the team and your own responsibility. More emphasis on the Lead position. 

Otherwise, there is a dissonance between an excellent self-presentation and a case presentation.
